533
00:54:15,136 --> 00:54:17,052
Kita berdua?

534
00:54:17,104 --> 00:54:19,471
Itu gila, bukan?

535
00:54:19,523 --> 00:54:22,775
Kita harus mencoba.

536
00:54:22,810 --> 00:54:26,528
