550
00:55:36,884 --> 00:55:39,601
Ternyata aku salah.

551
00:55:48,612 --> 00:55:50,562
Apa kau senang?

552
00:55:58,739 --> 00:56:04,960
Kukira aku tak bisa senang lagi, tapi

